name: StreamNetworkServiceTypeValue
desc: NSStream defines these string constants for specifying the service type of a stream.

items.name: static let background: StreamNetworkServiceTypeValue
items.desc: Specifies that the stream is providing a background service.

items.name: static let video: StreamNetworkServiceTypeValue
items.desc: Specifies that the stream is providing video service.

items.name: static let voice: StreamNetworkServiceTypeValue
items.desc: Specifies that the stream is providing voice service.

items.name: static let voIP: StreamNetworkServiceTypeValue
items.desc: Specifies that the stream is providing VoIP service.
